<h2>NatsuLion</h2>
<div class="text">
<h3>About NatsuLion</h3>
<p>
NatsuLion is a Twitter client for Mac OSX. Currently in its beta state.<br/>

Note: Leopard (10.5) is required.
</p>

Its goals are the follows:
<ul>
  <li>Be simple</li>
  <li>Feature icons</li>
  <li>Easy to use for Twitter light users</li>
</ul>
You can <a href="http://www.physalis.net/NatsuLion/NatsuLion.zip">download</a> the latest version from.

</p>
<p>
<img src="images/ss1.png" alt="screen shot 1">
</p>

<h3>Main Functions</h3>
<p>
<ul>
  <li>Display your friend timeline</li>
  <li>Post a message</li>
  <li>Create a favorite</li>
  <li>Replies including messages contain @<my ID> are emphasized</li>
  <li>Input support for "@&lt;ID&gt;". By clicking icon, @&lt;ID&gt; apears in the message input field</li>
  <li>Growl Notifications (replies are notified with a higher priority and stickied)</li>
</ul>  
</p>

<h3>Known Problems</h3>
<p>
<ul>
  <li>need to improve auto resizing textfield for message input <a href="http://jira.physalis.net/browse/NTLN-27">[NTLN-27]</a></li>
</ul>
Please refer <a href="http://jira.physalis.net/browse/NTLN">http://jira.physalis.net/browse/NTLN</a> for details.
</p>

<h3>License</h3>
<p>
NatsuLion is published under the <a href="http://www.physalis.net/repos/natsulion/trunk/LICENSE">Modified BSD</a> license and shipped with <a href="http://sparkle.andymatuschak.org/">Sparkle</a> and <a href="http://growl.info/">Growl</a> . Please find these licenses <a href="http://www.physalis.net/repos/natsulion/trunk/licenses/">here</a>.
</p>

<h3>Source Code</h3>
<p>
<a href="http://www.physalis.net/repos/natsulion/trunk/">http://www.physalis.net/repos/natsulion/trunk/</a>
